1
00:00:01,130 --> 00:00:02,500
Makoto...

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,130
Hm?

3
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:07,630
You've got something on your face.

4
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:09,380
Huh? Where?

5
00:00:10,510 --> 00:00:11,510
A grain of rice.

6
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:12,740
How embarrassing!

7
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:15,770
Don't tell me it's been there
since Natsu-san was here.

8
00:00:18,730 --> 00:00:21,020
You're really into her, huh?

9
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:23,940
No, it's just... it was our first time meeting.

10
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:27,070
I didn't think someone like Natsu
would be your type.

11
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:28,950
You're into that type too?

12
00:00:28,950 --> 00:00:30,280
No, that's not what I said.

13
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,410
Because the last girl who dumped you
was a completely different type.

14
00:00:33,410 --> 00:00:35,120
I see. So you'll go for anyone.

15
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:37,620
What? What kind of person do you take me for?

16
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:39,370
That's so disrespectful to Natsu-san.

17
00:00:39,370 --> 00:00:41,540
It's all "Natsu-san" this, "Natsu-san" that...

18
00:00:41,540 --> 00:00:46,090
(Is he mad that I'm sizing up his girlfriend?)

19
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:48,800
Yuki, I'm sorry.
You have every right to be upset.

20
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:51,430
But that's not what I meant at all.

21
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:55,760
I hate it.

22
00:00:57,180 --> 00:00:59,130
When I heard Natsu say she'd vote for you,

23
00:00:59,130 --> 00:01:01,110
the way you were grinning from ear to ear...

24
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:02,940
- I couldn't stand watching it.
- Ow, that hurts! You're being too rough!

25
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:03,980
Whoa!
